The paper deals with query-focused summarization, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely categories. The paper also uses BERT, a popular deep learning model, for summarization, which falls under the subfield of deep learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses data augmentation, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.DL).
